Job Details
1. Uses different marketing techniques to increase the company’s brand value and awareness 2. Achieves marketing financial objectives by directly increasing sales 3. Implements strategic plans to meet customers' demands on HSE training, ISO Consultancy and management training, and Inspection services 4. Prepares business proposals for potential, new and existing clients across UAE 5. Organizes training (internal and external) and inspection schedules and venues for proper coordination and execution 6. Maintains and updates client database
Requirements
Bachelor's Degree  Good communication skills Fluent in English Preferably with experience in Sales & Marketing Preferably under family sponsorship
